data.description: A MUST SEE! Wonderful, 2020, 4,2,3 home in the prestigious rural subdivision of West Pecan Acres will not disappoint! Only 2 miles from Hwy 114, this beautiful property has everything you could want; 4 BR or 3 with beautiful office, spacious open concept living and dining area plus a chef's dream kitchen with ample cabinets and an oversized island. Featured in the living area is a WBFP. A gorgeous Master Suite and bath look out on the huge fenced backyard, just ready for a beautiful pool, shop or a garden. Perhaps just relaxing on the covered patio with cozy outdoor fireplace enjoying the quietness of the country is your idea of enjoyment. This property has it all!
